					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Many thanks to the following users for their feedback: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mr-abadede" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3050072&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="Mr Abadede" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3050072)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mr-abadede" >Mr Abadede</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jayrassicpark" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2924850&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="JayrassicPark" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2924850)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jayrassicpark" >JayrassicPark</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/unoriginalusername" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2975376&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1511563502" alt="UnoriginalUsername" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2975376)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/unoriginalusername" >UnoriginalUsername</a></span>.</p> <p>Image is a public domain work by <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Meleagros_Antikensammlung_Berlin_Sk215_n2.jpg">Bibi Saint-Pol</a>.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;Explanation&nbsp;in&nbsp;case&nbsp;you&nbsp;didn't&nbsp;get&nbsp;what&nbsp;this&nbsp;skip's&nbsp;about</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">◀&nbsp;Collapse</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>In a parallel dimension where everybody keeps anomalous pets, a bunch of scammers pretended to be a high end pet hotel and saved on expenses by teleporting their clients to Earth for the Foundation to take care of, before teleporting them back to their unsuspecting owners.</p> <p>The mysterious caller caught on to this scam and decided to confront the scammers, who denied being the masterminds and distracted her with Site-19's phone number, so she would be busy going after the Foundation while they bring back all the pets and make their escape.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
